<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Certificate of Satisfactory Performance</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #e8e8e8;
  }
  .page {
    max-width: 850px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 30px 50px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #000;
  }
  .letterhead-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .date-line {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .title {
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: underline;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  p {
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    text-align: justify;
  }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 10px 0 12px 0;
  }
  table th, table td {
    border: 1px solid #000;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  table th {
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  table td {
    height: 24px;
  }
  .signoff {
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .signoff p {
    margin: 1px 0;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .seal {
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <p class="letterhead-note">(To be issued on the Customer's Official Letterhead)</p>

  <p class="date-line">Date: _________________________</p>

  <div class="title">CERTIFICATE OF SATISFACTORY PERFORMANCE</div>

  <p>
    This is to certify that the products supplied by Laser Power &amp; Infra Limited (CIN:
    U14220WB1988PLC043591), having its Registered Office at Room 307, 4A Pollock
    Street, Kolkata – 700001, West Bengal, Corporate Office at Adventz Infinity@5, BN
    Block, 19th Floor – North Wing, Sector-V, Salt Lake, Kolkata – 700091, West Bengal, and
    Manufacturing Units at Poly Park, Howrah – 711302, West Bengal and Plot No. F1, P.O.
    Jakpur, Vidyasagar Industrial Park, Kharagpur, Paschim Medinipur – 721301, West
    Bengal, against our Purchase Order No. {{partyRefNo}} dated {{partyRefDate}} executed
    for {{partyName}} had been received and utilized for our project
    requirements supplied during the period {{formatFY fy}}, amounting to a
    total value of Rs. {{invoiceAmt}} (Rupees Only).
  </p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:10%;">Sl No</th>
        <th style="width:45%;">Item</th>
        <th style="width:20%;">Quantity</th>
        <th style="width:25%;">Date</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{#each items}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{inc @index}}</td>
        <td>{{this.itemName}}</td>
        <td>{{this.invoiceQty}}</td>
        <td>{{this.saleBillDate}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>
    Based on our experience, the supplied products were received in good condition, met
    our purchase requirements and have been performing satisfactorily during service.
  </p>

  <p>
    We are satisfied with the quality of the products, delivery performance and the
    professional support provided by Laser Power &amp; Infra Limited during the execution of
    the order.
  </p>

  <p>
    We have been procuring various products from Laser Power &amp; Infra Limited for our
    project requirements and find them to be a reliable supplier.
  </p>

  <p>Thanking you,</p>

  <div class="signoff">
    <p>For </p>
    <p>Authorised Signatory</p>
    <p>Name: </p>
    <p>Designation: </p>
    <p class="seal">Company Seal</p>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
